test:
  commands:
    - python -c "import numpy; numpy.show_config()"
    - python -c "import scipy, sys; sys.exit(not scipy.test(verbose=1, label='fast',
      tests=None, extra_argv=['-k', 'not (_not_a_real_test or test_x0_equals_Mb[bicgstab
      or test_failure_to_run_iterations or (test_lsq_linear and test_large_rank_deficient)
      or (test_iterative and test_precond_inverse[case1]) or (test_optimize and TestBrute
      and test_workers) or (TestLevyStable and test_location_scale[pdf-1]) or (test_propack
      and test_examples))', '-nauto', '--timeout=1200', '--durations=50']))"
  requires:
    - mpmath
    - pytest
    - pytest-timeout
    - pytest-xdist
